    "media:imagetext": "Take the Path that Leads to Adventure\nCustom-made Asia Vacations at Package Prices\nNow is a great time to visit Asia, and Northwest Airlines\nWorldVacations™ can take you there at very affordable\nprices. From the gold leaf-covered temples of Bangkok, to\nthe views from China's Great Wall, WorldVacations has a\npackage to Asia for you. WorldVacations offers fantastic\nair and land packages to:\nv Hong Kong\nv Beijing\nv Bangkok\nv Tokyo\nv Singapore\nv Shanghai\nWorldVacations Packages to Asia Include:\nRoundtrip, Coach Class air transportation via nonstop\nand connecting service on Northwest Airlines\nRoundtrip transfers between airport and hotel\nHalf-day sightseeing tour\n• Choice of hotel accommodations\n• Hotel taxes and service charges\n• 2.000 WorldVacations WorldPerks® Bonus Miles in\naddition to actual miles flown\n• And more!\nFor more details, call your professional\ntravel agent or World Vacations at\n1-800-800-1504\nReservation Hours: 7:30 am-8:00 pm (CST) \u003e Monday— Friday\n©1999 Northwest Airlines Inc.\nwww.nwa.com\nNORTHWEST\nAIRLINES\nWorld Vacations\nWVMS7805",
