      "NORTHWEST\nAIRLINES\nFlight\nSchedule\nEffective\nJune 2,\n1999-\nSept. 7,\n1999\nFor\nNonstop\nand Direct\nFlights\nCall Northwest\nAirlines at\n1-800-225-2525,\npurchase tickets\nonline at\nwww.nwa.com,\nor call your\ntravel agent.\nKLM\nOSAKA, JAPAN\nABI\nSM",
